{"tid":2185833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友成日唔記得我嘅好。。","createTime":"2020-09-02T13:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T14:59:49.000Z","uid":319048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"815096ecc348ea2bd32b81dab9e8b910ea0aaa45","tid":2185833,"uid":319048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"我同佢一齊左就嚟半年<br />\n佢平時好鐘意扭計同發脾氣，咁我都冇乜所謂。<br />\n但佢好似有d得吋進尺，是咁的，我平時基本上我冇野做嘅話我一定會接佢收工，佢住上水嗰邊，而我就住油尖旺，我平時第二日唔洗翻工嘅話我9成都係會送佢翻去。咁有一日佢翻工，而我聽日都要翻工，我就好似平時咁送到車站，佢發脾氣。佢因為咁而發我脾氣，但我平時放工早嘅話都會問佢肚唔肚餓 洗唔洗買野食俾佢。但呢d佢好似冇放喺眼內，淨係會諗我嘅唔好。我仲應唔應該為佢付出。。。"},{"pid":"08f683f82c4eb3b5968b4b01fb3150f4d7c36b0b","tid":2185833,"uid":199162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3bb28cc77a053f3674bd0128b225c4e2a93bdf","tid":2185833,"uid":319048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f683f82c4eb3b5968b4b01fb3150f4d7c36b0b","tid":2185833,"uid":199162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"咁而家點算 佢已經習慣左我嘅好咁 只會挑剔"},{"pid":"ce145ecb143d2edc3a2db9782c1629a8e3425887","tid":2185833,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb3bb28cc77a053f3674bd0128b225c4e2a93bdf","tid":2185833,"uid":319048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f683f82c4eb3b5968b4b01fb3150f4d7c36b0b","tid":2185833,"uid":199162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"咁而家點算 佢已經習慣左我嘅好咁 只會挑剔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}